			<![CDATA[<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Hi.  When did you get back?"/>
<b>B:</b>	Late last night.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="So, how was the flight?"/>
<b>B:</b>	Long.  And pretty bumpy.  I didn’t get any sleep.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="That’s too bad.  So tell me, how was the weather?"/>
<b>B:</b>	It was terrible.  Cold and rainy.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="What about the food?"/>
<b>B:</b>	It was OK.  Nothing special.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="What did you do?"/>
<b>B:</b>	I went to lots of museums.
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="How was that?"/>
<b>B:</b>	It was pretty boring, actually.]]>
